WEBVTT

00:00:00.750 --> 00:00:01.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ISKA] Get down!
-[gunfire]</b></Default>

00:00:02.169 --> 00:00:03.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Iska grunting]</b></Default>

00:00:04.589 --> 00:00:05.589 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah.</b></Default>

00:00:06.049 --> 00:00:07.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

00:00:07.219 --> 00:00:09.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:00:09.640 --> 00:00:10.589 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIZERHYBY]
Finally.</b></Default>

00:00:10.679 --> 00:00:12.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got one of you to show.</b></Default>

00:00:12.550 --> 00:00:14.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fall back!
Go without me!</b></Default>

00:00:14.640 --> 00:00:16.059 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MISMIS]
No, we won't!</b></Default>

00:00:16.140 --> 00:00:17.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be fine.</b></Default>

00:00:17.350 --> 00:00:19.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can handle this.
Now, go!</b></Default>

00:00:19.649 --> 00:00:22.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:00:22.809 --> 00:00:25.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I see, you're former
Saint Disciple Iska</b></Default>

00:00:25.399 --> 00:00:26.859 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-aren't you?
-[laughs]</b></Default>

00:00:26.940 --> 00:00:29.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you here
to rescue a helpless girl.</b></Default>

00:00:29.149 --> 00:00:31.739 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or are you here
to steal my exquisite earring?</b></Default>

00:00:31.989 --> 00:00:33.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where is Sisbell?</b></Default>

00:00:33.700 --> 00:00:36.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIZERHYBY]
Yes, where is she, indeed?</b></Default>

00:00:36.579 --> 00:00:38.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] [gasps]
What's that light?</b></Default>

00:00:40.369 --> 00:00:41.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIZERHYBY]
If you survive this</b></Default>

00:00:41.789 --> 00:00:44.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll make you
a glowing pawn, too.</b></Default>

00:00:44.799 --> 00:00:46.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[fingers snap]
-[ISKA] Ready.</b></Default>

00:00:47.130 --> 00:00:48.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For the glory!</b></Default>

00:01:09.530 --> 00:01:14.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}OUR LAST CRUSADE OR
THE RISE OF A NEW WORLD</b></Default>

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:22.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER]
Hydra, this has gone too far.</b></Default>

00:02:22.310 --> 00:02:24.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not your disrespectful
treatment</b></Default>

00:02:24.099 --> 00:02:25.979 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the people's Queen</b></Default>

00:02:26.310 --> 00:02:28.229 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How dare you attack Mira!</b></Default>

00:02:28.689 --> 00:02:30.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}-Who gave you the right?!
-[explosion] -[screen shatters]</b></Default>

00:02:30.650 --> 00:02:32.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You brought upheaval
to the Sovereignty</b></Default>

00:02:32.490 --> 00:02:33.569 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with your slight.</b></Default>

00:02:33.650 --> 00:02:35.319 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You will reap what you sow.</b></Default>

00:02:35.409 --> 00:02:38.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall expose your actions
for the world to see!</b></Default>

00:02:40.370 --> 00:02:42.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come forth!
If you have knowledge</b></Default>

00:02:42.370 --> 00:02:45.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of Gregorio's secret spell</b></Default>

00:02:46.419 --> 00:02:48.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So the spell is above us?</b></Default>

00:02:48.379 --> 00:02:49.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm done with you!</b></Default>

00:02:49.629 --> 00:02:51.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fir roaring]</b></Default>

00:02:53.919 --> 00:02:56.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VICHYSSOISE]
The planet is rife with anger.</b></Default>

00:02:56.430 --> 00:02:57.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where's the spell?</b></Default>

00:02:57.849 --> 00:02:58.969 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it here?
[tapping]</b></Default>

00:02:59.050 --> 00:03:00.139 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not here.</b></Default>

00:03:00.219 --> 00:03:02.349 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But this is where you will die.</b></Default>

00:03:02.469 --> 00:03:04.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Great
"Salinger the Transcendent?"</b></Default>

00:03:05.310 --> 00:03:07.439 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yum</b></Default>

00:03:07.520 --> 00:03:09.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a shame
I'll have to evaporate you.</b></Default>

00:03:10.439 --> 00:03:11.819 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here's what's happening.</b></Default>

00:03:11.900 --> 00:03:14.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've heard
of Tri-Stage, Fusion.</b></Default>

00:03:14.189 --> 00:03:15.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you have
a powerful human</b></Default>

00:03:16.069 --> 00:03:18.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and they become one
with an astral spirit</b></Default>

00:03:18.530 --> 00:03:21.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they transcend
to a new level of mage.</b></Default>

00:03:21.449 --> 00:03:23.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the entire history
of this planet</b></Default>

00:03:23.789 --> 00:03:26.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>only two people were able
to achieve this feat.</b></Default>

00:03:26.750 --> 00:03:30.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Founder Nebulis</b></Default>

00:03:30.710 --> 00:03:32.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For decades</b></Default>

00:03:32.590 --> 00:03:34.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to achieve fusion
for themselves.</b></Default>

00:03:34.550 --> 00:03:37.009 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Including experimenting
on their own people.</b></Default>

00:03:37.259 --> 00:03:39.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you're one
of their test subjects.</b></Default>

00:03:39.639 --> 00:03:41.139 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's Vichyssoise.</b></Default>

00:03:41.599 --> 00:03:43.719 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hate being called
a test subject.</b></Default>

00:03:43.810 --> 00:03:45.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Use my name, will ya?</b></Default>

00:03:45.520 --> 00:03:47.689 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER] Oh, you want me
to remember your name?</b></Default>

00:03:47.770 --> 00:03:50.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your arrogance is too great
for your own good, girl.</b></Default>

00:03:50.689 --> 00:03:51.819 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll pass.</b></Default>

00:03:51.900 --> 00:03:53.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Man.</b></Default>

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:54.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How sad.</b></Default>

00:03:55.110 --> 00:03:57.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A has-been mage</b></Default>

00:03:58.069 --> 00:04:00.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as though their curtain
hadn't dropped.</b></Default>

00:04:00.780 --> 00:04:02.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You haven't got a clue, girl.</b></Default>

00:04:02.830 --> 00:04:05.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at me</b></Default>

00:04:05.159 --> 00:04:07.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The stage comes to life
around me!</b></Default>

00:04:07.460 --> 00:04:09.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hear me, I shall say it again.
-[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:12.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, I think I've earned
a round of applause!</b></Default>

00:04:12.629 --> 00:04:14.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[electricity crackling]
-[explosion]</b></Default>

00:04:14.250 --> 00:04:15.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasps]</b></Default>

00:04:15.340 --> 00:04:17.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's going on here?!</b></Default>

00:04:17.129 --> 00:04:18.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[rumbling]
-[CYSTEA] It's Salinger.</b></Default>

00:04:19.300 --> 00:04:20.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Salinger.</b></Default>

00:04:20.639 --> 00:04:22.509 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Jhin, do you remember
that name?</b></Default>

00:04:22.720 --> 00:04:23.889 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not a bit.</b></Default>

00:04:23.970 --> 00:04:26.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And since we don't</b></Default>

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:28.639 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMI] "Big deal"
doesn't do him justice!</b></Default>

00:04:28.939 --> 00:04:30.189 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's dangerous.</b></Default>

00:04:30.269 --> 00:04:32.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The man's our nation's
most-wanted criminal!</b></Default>

00:04:33.189 --> 00:04:34.319 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thirty years ago</b></Default>

00:04:34.399 --> 00:04:36.819 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he's the one
who attacked our former Queen!</b></Default>

00:04:37.149 --> 00:04:39.569 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMI] Cystea, surely</b></Default>

00:04:39.660 --> 00:04:41.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Soldiers are shouting his name.</b></Default>

00:04:42.029 --> 00:04:45.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Captain Mismis, the enemy's
security is occupied.</b></Default>

00:04:45.790 --> 00:04:47.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now's our chance to escape!</b></Default>

00:04:47.829 --> 00:04:49.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

00:04:49.290 --> 00:04:51.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right.
Let's evacuate, fast.</b></Default>

00:04:51.329 --> 00:04:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

00:04:52.959 --> 00:04:55.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] There was a large
explosion at Snow the Sun?!</b></Default>

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:58.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Lady Alice, please</b></Default>

00:04:58.470 --> 00:04:59.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, Sisbell...</b></Default>

00:05:00.509 --> 00:05:02.089 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Does that mean they were found?</b></Default>

00:05:02.220 --> 00:05:03.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska and the others.</b></Default>

00:05:03.550 --> 00:05:04.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are they all right?</b></Default>

00:05:05.100 --> 00:05:07.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN]
This is a serious problem.</b></Default>

00:05:07.560 --> 00:05:08.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

00:05:09.019 --> 00:05:11.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's only been a few days
since the Empire's assault.</b></Default>

00:05:12.230 --> 00:05:14.569 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One could assume there
may be soldiers in hiding.</b></Default>

00:05:14.730 --> 00:05:16.149 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You, come here, please.
-Sir?</b></Default>

00:05:16.230 --> 00:05:17.689 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Send in the guard.</b></Default>

00:05:18.029 --> 00:05:19.439 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SOLDIER 212A]
It's not the Empire.</b></Default>

00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:22.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-It's Salinger the Demon!
-[all gasps]</b></Default>

00:05:22.699 --> 00:05:24.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you certain
this is the truth?</b></Default>

00:05:24.779 --> 00:05:25.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SOLDIER 212A]
Yes, it's true.</b></Default>

00:05:26.120 --> 00:05:27.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The security cameras
got a positive</b></Default>

00:05:27.620 --> 00:05:29.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>facial recognition match.</b></Default>

00:05:30.540 --> 00:05:31.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Rin.
-What?</b></Default>

00:05:31.790 --> 00:05:33.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know nothing about this</b></Default>

00:05:33.959 --> 00:05:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The last time I ever saw him
was in Alcatroz.</b></Default>

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:38.339 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After he broke out of prison</b></Default>

00:05:38.420 --> 00:05:40.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no one was able
to track him down!</b></Default>

00:05:43.389 --> 00:05:44.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Salinger.</b></Default>

00:05:44.850 --> 00:05:47.009 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What have you done, and why?</b></Default>

00:05:47.970 --> 00:05:50.389 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] If Salinger's been
off the grid for this long</b></Default>

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:52.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why has he chosen
to show up now?</b></Default>

00:05:52.350 --> 00:05:53.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clapping]</b></Default>

00:05:54.350 --> 00:05:56.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's continue our meeting.</b></Default>

00:05:56.360 --> 00:05:57.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've identified the culprit.</b></Default>

00:05:58.069 --> 00:05:59.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our forces will maintain order.</b></Default>

00:06:00.860 --> 00:06:02.319 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)]
That's quite unlike you.</b></Default>

00:06:02.399 --> 00:06:03.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

00:06:03.529 --> 00:06:05.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The infamous demon
hides for years.</b></Default>

00:06:05.490 --> 00:06:07.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would he suddenly
launch an attack now?</b></Default>

00:06:08.120 --> 00:06:10.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a question
we should all ask.</b></Default>

00:06:10.120 --> 00:06:12.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And one you would
normally ask first.</b></Default>

00:06:12.709 --> 00:06:15.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He targets Snow the Sun</b></Default>

00:06:15.540 --> 00:06:17.089 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps you know his motive?</b></Default>

00:06:17.170 --> 00:06:19.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no idea
what he's after.</b></Default>

00:06:19.459 --> 00:06:20.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll catch him</b></Default>

00:06:20.459 --> 00:06:22.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then interrogate him
until we find out.</b></Default>

00:06:23.300 --> 00:06:25.509 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think your men
can catch that demon?</b></Default>

00:06:26.050 --> 00:06:27.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're prepared for anything.</b></Default>

00:06:28.139 --> 00:06:29.889 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Empire could strike
at any moment</b></Default>

00:06:29.970 --> 00:06:31.389 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so we've been ready.</b></Default>

00:06:33.060 --> 00:06:34.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Not good.</b></Default>

00:06:34.389 --> 00:06:37.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That means he'll be prepared
to fight off Iska and his team.</b></Default>

00:06:39.689 --> 00:06:41.529 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire roaring]</b></Default>

00:06:43.529 --> 00:06:45.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

00:06:46.370 --> 00:06:49.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm</b></Default>

00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:51.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was enhanced
by three levels, at the best.</b></Default>

00:06:52.410 --> 00:06:54.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, get up
and fight like you mean it!</b></Default>

00:06:54.920 --> 00:06:56.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How long are you
going to feign defeat?</b></Default>

00:06:57.129 --> 00:06:58.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vichyssoise did warn me.</b></Default>

00:06:59.170 --> 00:07:01.089 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said never assume
you've won</b></Default>

00:07:01.300 --> 00:07:04.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even if you have sliced him
into a dozen pieces.</b></Default>

00:07:04.129 --> 00:07:06.009 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>make sure he's actually dead.</b></Default>

00:07:08.639 --> 00:07:10.509 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's rather extreme.</b></Default>

00:07:11.720 --> 00:07:13.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My goodness, you are alive!</b></Default>

00:07:13.930 --> 00:07:15.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you sure
you're not immortal?</b></Default>

00:07:16.019 --> 00:07:17.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Positive.</b></Default>

00:07:17.439 --> 00:07:19.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Also, I'm hurt.</b></Default>

00:07:19.899 --> 00:07:21.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wasn't pretending.</b></Default>

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:23.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Is she able to channel
her astral energy</b></Default>

00:07:23.569 --> 00:07:24.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>through another mage's spirit?</b></Default>

00:07:25.029 --> 00:07:26.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those flames.</b></Default>

00:07:26.110 --> 00:07:28.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her ability did more than
just enhance the attack.</b></Default>

00:07:28.819 --> 00:07:31.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Trying to figure out
what my ability might be?</b></Default>

00:07:31.579 --> 00:07:32.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

00:07:32.579 --> 00:07:34.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The more you know</b></Default>

00:07:34.500 --> 00:07:35.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and you'll second-guess
yourself.</b></Default>

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:37.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

00:07:37.170 --> 00:07:38.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIZERHYBY] And when you
second-guess yourself</b></Default>

00:07:39.079 --> 00:07:40.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-you die.
-[earing clanking]</b></Default>

00:07:40.959 --> 00:07:42.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, there's more?!</b></Default>

00:07:43.959 --> 00:07:47.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, sir, and pretty soon</b></Default>

00:07:47.220 --> 00:07:48.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fingers snap]</b></Default>

00:07:50.680 --> 00:07:51.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mines?</b></Default>

00:07:52.259 --> 00:07:53.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire roaring]</b></Default>

00:07:53.930 --> 00:07:54.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

00:07:55.019 --> 00:07:56.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm pulling out
all the stops by using</b></Default>

00:07:56.939 --> 00:07:59.189 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>two pawns for one
measly assassin.</b></Default>

00:07:59.269 --> 00:08:01.399 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Too warm of a welcome, perhaps?</b></Default>

00:08:02.019 --> 00:08:04.149 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

00:08:04.689 --> 00:08:06.899 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No! What? You
withstood that, too?!</b></Default>

00:08:06.990 --> 00:08:08.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]
Did you think...</b></Default>

00:08:09.069 --> 00:08:10.779 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-...you got me?!</b></Default>

00:08:11.069 --> 00:08:12.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sword clanks]</b></Default>

00:08:12.910 --> 00:08:14.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh!</b></Default>

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:18.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Too close for comfort.</b></Default>

00:08:19.079 --> 00:08:20.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just close enough.</b></Default>

00:08:21.839 --> 00:08:23.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Return my earring, fiend!</b></Default>

00:08:23.709 --> 00:08:26.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why? It can't be
that important, right?</b></Default>

00:08:27.129 --> 00:08:28.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's mine!</b></Default>

00:08:28.379 --> 00:08:30.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:08:30.839 --> 00:08:32.889 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've both got something
each other wants!</b></Default>

00:08:33.009 --> 00:08:34.309 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Keep that in mind!</b></Default>

00:08:35.679 --> 00:08:37.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

00:08:38.440 --> 00:08:40.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You and your astral art
are pretty</b></Default>

00:08:40.100 --> 00:08:42.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but thankfully</b></Default>

00:08:42.440 --> 00:08:44.529 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here, this is how you
turn up the heat!</b></Default>

00:08:44.899 --> 00:08:45.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[taps]</b></Default>

00:08:46.279 --> 00:08:47.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:08:49.029 --> 00:08:50.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER] Do not attack me
with your filthy</b></Default>

00:08:50.779 --> 00:08:52.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>synthetic flame.</b></Default>

00:08:53.700 --> 00:08:55.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VICHYSSOISE]
What a tool!</b></Default>

00:08:56.289 --> 00:08:59.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An astral mage
can't summon flames like this.</b></Default>

00:08:59.539 --> 00:09:01.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It doesn't matter
if the Founder's blood</b></Default>

00:09:01.379 --> 00:09:02.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is flowing through your veins</b></Default>

00:09:02.789 --> 00:09:05.299 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or if you're the most talented
mage on this planet.</b></Default>

00:09:05.590 --> 00:09:08.009 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing compares
to the power of a witch</b></Default>

00:09:08.090 --> 00:09:10.179 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>fused with an astral spirit!</b></Default>

00:09:11.090 --> 00:09:12.179 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:09:12.679 --> 00:09:14.809 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have one trick</b></Default>

00:09:15.389 --> 00:09:16.639 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

00:09:18.350 --> 00:09:20.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Say what you will, mage.</b></Default>

00:09:20.190 --> 00:09:21.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must know you're done!</b></Default>

00:09:22.100 --> 00:09:23.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your Water-Reflection skill</b></Default>

00:09:23.559 --> 00:09:25.519 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can siphon power
from astral spirits</b></Default>

00:09:25.610 --> 00:09:27.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the royals
may fear you for it.</b></Default>

00:09:27.570 --> 00:09:30.149 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But please</b></Default>

00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:32.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your ability is weak.</b></Default>

00:09:32.159 --> 00:09:33.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Especially compared to--</b></Default>

00:09:33.279 --> 00:09:36.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are the epitome of naivety</b></Default>

00:09:36.289 --> 00:09:38.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you have no semblance
or grace.</b></Default>

00:09:38.539 --> 00:09:40.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not surprising
from a girl like you.</b></Default>

00:09:41.159 --> 00:09:42.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've seen the tip
of the spear</b></Default>

00:09:43.210 --> 00:09:45.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>yet you're still cocky enough
to assume you know</b></Default>

00:09:45.289 --> 00:09:47.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the full extent of my power?
[sighs]</b></Default>

00:09:48.049 --> 00:09:50.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VICHYSSOISE] You've got
my attention, pretty boy!</b></Default>

00:09:50.299 --> 00:09:51.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Incinerating you too soon
would be</b></Default>

00:09:51.970 --> 00:09:53.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a mighty waste
of our entanglement.</b></Default>

00:09:54.049 --> 00:09:57.139 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's see how you handle
the sting of my Magic Bullet!</b></Default>

00:09:57.679 --> 00:09:59.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Astral spirit
of exploding earth</b></Default>

00:10:00.019 --> 00:10:02.639 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>blast from the earth
with your tectonic rage!</b></Default>

00:10:02.730 --> 00:10:03.899 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

00:10:03.980 --> 00:10:06.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER] A performer
has many hidden talents.</b></Default>

00:10:06.399 --> 00:10:09.529 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-All of which can kill you.
-Shut up!</b></Default>

00:10:09.690 --> 00:10:10.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're pathetic.</b></Default>

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:14.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're just a monster
who's all bark and no bite.</b></Default>

00:10:14.570 --> 00:10:15.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

00:10:15.700 --> 00:10:17.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER]
Hmm. She's gone.</b></Default>

00:10:17.409 --> 00:10:19.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who possessed
the skill to infiltrate</b></Default>

00:10:19.409 --> 00:10:21.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this facility before I did?</b></Default>

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:24.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
Snow?</b></Default>

00:10:24.419 --> 00:10:26.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL]
Imperial soldier!</b></Default>

00:10:26.210 --> 00:10:27.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stop right there!</b></Default>

00:10:27.789 --> 00:10:28.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Grugell?!</b></Default>

00:10:28.840 --> 00:10:30.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:32.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL]
Hm. You.</b></Default>

00:10:32.129 --> 00:10:34.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're the ex-Saint Disciple.</b></Default>

00:10:34.129 --> 00:10:35.639 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska, was it?</b></Default>

00:10:36.639 --> 00:10:37.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

00:10:39.309 --> 00:10:40.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

00:10:43.850 --> 00:10:45.649 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

00:10:46.399 --> 00:10:48.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL]
You're going to regret using me</b></Default>

00:10:48.360 --> 00:10:49.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for your own gain.</b></Default>

00:10:49.779 --> 00:10:50.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Using you?</b></Default>

00:10:50.899 --> 00:10:52.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you talking about?</b></Default>

00:10:52.570 --> 00:10:55.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>While I'd love to soak in
the sight of your discomfort</b></Default>

00:10:55.909 --> 00:10:57.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a few bones to pick</b></Default>

00:10:57.279 --> 00:10:59.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with those little
friends of yours.</b></Default>

00:10:59.580 --> 00:11:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They shall die.</b></Default>

00:11:01.330 --> 00:11:02.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pierce him!</b></Default>

00:11:04.500 --> 00:11:05.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[grunts]
-[shatters]</b></Default>

00:11:06.250 --> 00:11:07.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, release!</b></Default>

00:11:08.210 --> 00:11:09.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL] [gasps]
It can't be.</b></Default>

00:11:10.090 --> 00:11:12.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are these Mizerhyby's flames?!</b></Default>

00:11:12.259 --> 00:11:14.009 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Curse you, disciple!</b></Default>

00:11:17.299 --> 00:11:18.299 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-[thwacks]</b></Default>

00:11:18.759 --> 00:11:20.929 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can finish
this on the battlefield.</b></Default>

00:11:22.350 --> 00:11:23.389 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

00:11:24.519 --> 00:11:25.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice.</b></Default>

00:11:25.980 --> 00:11:27.149 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you learned of any news</b></Default>

00:11:27.230 --> 00:11:28.809 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in Sisbell's rescue effort?</b></Default>

00:11:29.480 --> 00:11:30.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, not yet.</b></Default>

00:11:31.110 --> 00:11:33.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If there was an update</b></Default>

00:11:33.990 --> 00:11:35.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, I see.</b></Default>

00:11:36.240 --> 00:11:38.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mother</b></Default>

00:11:38.279 --> 00:11:39.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I can't stop
thinking about.</b></Default>

00:11:41.200 --> 00:11:42.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>About Salinger, right?</b></Default>

00:11:42.789 --> 00:11:44.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Yes.
Why is he here?</b></Default>

00:11:44.960 --> 00:11:47.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And why is he attacking
Snow the Sun?</b></Default>

00:11:47.620 --> 00:11:49.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't have
the slightest idea.</b></Default>

00:11:50.129 --> 00:11:53.009 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The incident 30 years ago
ended our relationship.</b></Default>

00:11:53.379 --> 00:11:55.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't tell you
what's going through his mind</b></Default>

00:11:55.340 --> 00:11:56.679 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after all these years.</b></Default>

00:11:56.759 --> 00:11:59.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:11:59.139 --> 00:12:01.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To think, the man
who attacked the Queen</b></Default>

00:12:01.139 --> 00:12:02.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>escaped because of me.</b></Default>

00:12:02.809 --> 00:12:05.179 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was unable to stop
the Empire.</b></Default>

00:12:05.269 --> 00:12:07.309 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I could not quell
the minister's fears</b></Default>

00:12:07.389 --> 00:12:08.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>during the meeting.</b></Default>

00:12:09.559 --> 00:12:10.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A true shame.</b></Default>

00:12:10.690 --> 00:12:12.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am unfit to be Queen.</b></Default>

00:12:12.440 --> 00:12:13.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh. That's not true!</b></Default>

00:12:14.070 --> 00:12:15.149 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't say that!</b></Default>

00:12:15.240 --> 00:12:16.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice...</b></Default>

00:12:16.279 --> 00:12:18.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>losing the Queen's election
is not an option.</b></Default>

00:12:19.029 --> 00:12:20.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you fail to win</b></Default>

00:12:20.409 --> 00:12:22.779 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Sovereignty as we know
it could collapse.</b></Default>

00:12:23.039 --> 00:12:25.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hear you</b></Default>

00:12:25.539 --> 00:12:26.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for the future.</b></Default>

00:12:26.659 --> 00:12:27.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Truly, I do.</b></Default>

00:12:28.169 --> 00:12:29.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, Mother...</b></Default>

00:12:32.419 --> 00:12:33.799 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, keep your chin up.</b></Default>

00:12:34.090 --> 00:12:35.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need you to keep going.</b></Default>

00:12:36.259 --> 00:12:37.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To save the Sovereignty</b></Default>

00:12:37.470 --> 00:12:39.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there is still much
to accomplish.</b></Default>

00:12:40.340 --> 00:12:41.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like what?</b></Default>

00:12:42.009 --> 00:12:43.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>While I work on saving Sibell</b></Default>

00:12:44.429 --> 00:12:46.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need to remain close
to support you.</b></Default>

00:12:46.639 --> 00:12:51.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:12:51.360 --> 00:12:53.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] I don't want to feel
the way I did before.</b></Default>

00:12:53.899 --> 00:12:55.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The anger, the grief.</b></Default>

00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:56.899 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They make one irrational.</b></Default>

00:12:59.450 --> 00:13:02.779 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The truth is, I can't save
everything on my own.</b></Default>

00:13:03.200 --> 00:13:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Imperial Army's assault
forced me to realize that...</b></Default>

00:13:06.750 --> 00:13:09.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]
We're a team.</b></Default>

00:13:09.409 --> 00:13:10.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska.</b></Default>

00:13:11.289 --> 00:13:12.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All of us!</b></Default>

00:13:13.590 --> 00:13:15.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
I gotta keep moving, or else.</b></Default>

00:13:15.500 --> 00:13:16.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosions]</b></Default>

00:13:16.840 --> 00:13:17.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:13:18.340 --> 00:13:19.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

00:13:19.340 --> 00:13:20.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Huh?</b></Default>

00:13:20.509 --> 00:13:22.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIZERHYBY]
Former Saint Disciple.</b></Default>

00:13:22.340 --> 00:13:23.889 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You stole something of mine.</b></Default>

00:13:23.970 --> 00:13:24.889 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Iska scoffs]</b></Default>

00:13:24.970 --> 00:13:26.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I would like it back.</b></Default>

00:13:26.850 --> 00:13:28.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is this how you negotiate?</b></Default>

00:13:28.639 --> 00:13:29.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, dear.</b></Default>

00:13:29.980 --> 00:13:31.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do not negotiate
with insects!</b></Default>

00:13:32.059 --> 00:13:33.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I crush the life out of them!</b></Default>

00:13:34.149 --> 00:13:35.899 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Howlers! Kill him!
[fingers snap]</b></Default>

00:13:37.399 --> 00:13:38.899 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

00:13:39.190 --> 00:13:40.399 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sound attack?</b></Default>

00:13:41.320 --> 00:13:43.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[wailing]
-[groaning]</b></Default>

00:13:46.289 --> 00:13:47.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a smart move.</b></Default>

00:13:47.490 --> 00:13:48.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[slicing]</b></Default>

00:13:53.669 --> 00:13:55.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This wall should
block out the sound.</b></Default>

00:13:56.379 --> 00:13:57.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But still...</b></Default>

00:13:57.629 --> 00:13:58.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She knows exactly
where I'm at</b></Default>

00:13:59.049 --> 00:14:00.509 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'm as good as trapped.</b></Default>

00:14:01.129 --> 00:14:02.299 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:14:02.470 --> 00:14:04.139 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Explosion this time?
-[fire roaring]</b></Default>

00:14:05.100 --> 00:14:06.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

00:14:06.350 --> 00:14:07.889 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIZERHYBY]
This is just the beginning.</b></Default>

00:14:08.019 --> 00:14:10.929 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You haven't seen
the true power of my pawns yet.</b></Default>

00:14:11.230 --> 00:14:12.639 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Set ablaze.</b></Default>

00:14:13.019 --> 00:14:14.149 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sword clanks]</b></Default>

00:14:14.230 --> 00:14:15.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire roaring]</b></Default>

00:14:16.269 --> 00:14:18.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Uh-Huh!
-That almost killed me.</b></Default>

00:14:18.779 --> 00:14:20.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not falling for it again.</b></Default>

00:14:21.200 --> 00:14:23.529 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Release of Stars!</b></Default>

00:14:24.360 --> 00:14:25.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You vex me.</b></Default>

00:14:26.070 --> 00:14:28.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tranquility, sweep away!</b></Default>

00:14:28.539 --> 00:14:29.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

00:14:29.750 --> 00:14:31.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You Imperial worm!</b></Default>

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:34.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just how much power
are you going to make me use?</b></Default>

00:14:35.419 --> 00:14:37.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you die already!</b></Default>

00:14:38.590 --> 00:14:40.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh. No can do.</b></Default>

00:14:41.470 --> 00:14:42.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
This princess.</b></Default>

00:14:42.549 --> 00:14:44.179 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's extremely powerful.</b></Default>

00:14:44.259 --> 00:14:45.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And dangerous.</b></Default>

00:14:45.639 --> 00:14:47.679 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIZERHYBY] Attack him
with everything you've got.</b></Default>

00:14:47.970 --> 00:14:50.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't care
if you destroy the earring.</b></Default>

00:14:50.389 --> 00:14:52.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just make sure
to leave absolutely</b></Default>

00:14:52.309 --> 00:14:53.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no trace of this filth.</b></Default>

00:14:54.480 --> 00:14:55.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kill him!</b></Default>

00:14:55.559 --> 00:14:57.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire roaring]</b></Default>

00:14:59.190 --> 00:15:01.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Release Of Stars!</b></Default>

00:15:02.070 --> 00:15:03.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[air gusting]</b></Default>

00:15:04.659 --> 00:15:06.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

00:15:08.279 --> 00:15:09.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

00:15:10.240 --> 00:15:11.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something has interfered?</b></Default>

00:15:12.370 --> 00:15:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[electricity crackles]</b></Default>

00:15:14.710 --> 00:15:15.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
What just happened?</b></Default>

00:15:15.870 --> 00:15:17.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No.
Don't waver.</b></Default>

00:15:17.710 --> 00:15:19.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no time
to second-guess it!</b></Default>

00:15:21.129 --> 00:15:22.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:15:22.970 --> 00:15:24.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

00:15:28.259 --> 00:15:30.309 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VICHYSSOISE] Now you're just
enjoying yourself.</b></Default>

00:15:30.559 --> 00:15:33.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are old, demon</b></Default>

00:15:33.559 --> 00:15:35.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]
Oh, that's cute.</b></Default>

00:15:35.809 --> 00:15:38.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You turned back
into a human rather fast.</b></Default>

00:15:38.519 --> 00:15:40.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's wrong, my little witch?</b></Default>

00:15:40.149 --> 00:15:42.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't want the researchers
to see their ugly mistake?</b></Default>

00:15:43.279 --> 00:15:44.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will you shut up, grandpa?</b></Default>

00:15:45.279 --> 00:15:47.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll catch up with you
soon and end this!</b></Default>

00:15:47.740 --> 00:15:49.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your face irks me.</b></Default>

00:15:49.370 --> 00:15:50.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're done here.
[electricity crackling]</b></Default>

00:15:50.990 --> 00:15:52.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:15:52.370 --> 00:15:54.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be gone from this realm</b></Default>

00:15:54.409 --> 00:15:55.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[groans]
-[electricity crackling]</b></Default>

00:15:56.039 --> 00:15:59.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VICHYSSOISE] You're about
to see a real witch.</b></Default>

00:16:00.039 --> 00:16:01.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You will fear me.</b></Default>

00:16:01.710 --> 00:16:03.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that your attempt
at a curse?</b></Default>

00:16:04.259 --> 00:16:05.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire roaring]
[electricity crackling]</b></Default>

00:16:05.549 --> 00:16:08.799 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIZERHYBY] I grow tired
of all these uninvited guests.</b></Default>

00:16:08.889 --> 00:16:11.679 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER] Princess of Hydra</b></Default>

00:16:11.759 --> 00:16:13.679 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Give me Gregorio's
secret spell!</b></Default>

00:16:13.769 --> 00:16:14.929 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, that?</b></Default>

00:16:15.019 --> 00:16:16.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm afraid it's not here.</b></Default>

00:16:16.639 --> 00:16:18.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Missed it by a hair.</b></Default>

00:16:18.100 --> 00:16:18.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone stole it</b></Default>

00:16:19.019 --> 00:16:21.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just before
your grand entrance.</b></Default>

00:16:21.360 --> 00:16:22.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine.</b></Default>

00:16:22.360 --> 00:16:24.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then give me
the real secret spell.</b></Default>

00:16:24.399 --> 00:16:25.399 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIZERHYBY]
Huh?</b></Default>

00:16:25.779 --> 00:16:27.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER] You're trying
to tell me Hydra's blueprint</b></Default>

00:16:28.029 --> 00:16:29.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to create a monster was stolen?</b></Default>

00:16:29.950 --> 00:16:31.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't lie to me.</b></Default>

00:16:31.240 --> 00:16:32.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was just a replica</b></Default>

00:16:32.409 --> 00:16:34.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a fragment
of the real data.</b></Default>

00:16:35.000 --> 00:16:37.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have the original</b></Default>

00:16:37.710 --> 00:16:40.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You will demand
nothing from me!</b></Default>

00:16:40.750 --> 00:16:42.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ungrateful old rat!</b></Default>

00:16:42.419 --> 00:16:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will show you</b></Default>

00:16:43.340 --> 00:16:45.299 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the true power
of royal lineage!</b></Default>

00:16:45.590 --> 00:16:47.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Nobility comes not from blood</b></Default>

00:16:47.340 --> 00:16:49.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but from one's philosophy."</b></Default>

00:16:49.679 --> 00:16:52.429 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're blinded by
the arrogance of noble birth.</b></Default>

00:16:52.509 --> 00:16:54.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Having an astral spirit
means nothing</b></Default>

00:16:54.350 --> 00:16:55.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>without the will to grow it!</b></Default>

00:16:56.389 --> 00:16:57.639 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How can you claim the blood</b></Default>

00:16:57.730 --> 00:16:59.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you lack the courage?</b></Default>

00:16:59.440 --> 00:17:00.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

00:17:00.940 --> 00:17:02.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIZERHYBY]
You've a big mouth!</b></Default>

00:17:02.190 --> 00:17:04.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least</b></Default>

00:17:04.609 --> 00:17:05.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Claim whatever name you want</b></Default>

00:17:06.069 --> 00:17:07.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but do not speak down to me!
[electricity crackling]</b></Default>

00:17:07.819 --> 00:17:09.069 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire roaring]</b></Default>

00:17:09.490 --> 00:17:10.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where is the original?</b></Default>

00:17:11.279 --> 00:17:13.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like I'd ever reveal
that to you.</b></Default>

00:17:14.029 --> 00:17:17.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is where you'll die</b></Default>

00:17:17.700 --> 00:17:19.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SHANOROTTE]
Whatever it is, it's not good.</b></Default>

00:17:19.670 --> 00:17:22.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Snow the Sun glowed red</b></Default>

00:17:22.710 --> 00:17:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no idea
what's going on in there.</b></Default>

00:17:25.460 --> 00:17:26.589 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[COMM OFFICER 212A]
What about the demon?</b></Default>

00:17:26.670 --> 00:17:27.799 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or the Sun Royalty?</b></Default>

00:17:28.170 --> 00:17:30.089 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not seeing
anyone from here.</b></Default>

00:17:30.509 --> 00:17:32.299 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But still, it's intense.</b></Default>

00:17:32.390 --> 00:17:34.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seems that demon
and Mizerhyby may be</b></Default>

00:17:34.720 --> 00:17:36.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>settling a disagreement
with their fists.</b></Default>

00:17:37.390 --> 00:17:38.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My suggestion?</b></Default>

00:17:38.640 --> 00:17:40.519 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should fall back
immediately.</b></Default>

00:17:40.940 --> 00:17:42.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that is it from the field.</b></Default>

00:17:43.190 --> 00:17:44.309 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:17:44.650 --> 00:17:46.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

00:17:46.650 --> 00:17:48.779 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I'm so sorry about that.</b></Default>

00:17:48.940 --> 00:17:50.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's like people say...</b></Default>

00:17:50.109 --> 00:17:51.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"You're so tall</b></Default>

00:17:51.359 --> 00:17:53.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how much physical space
you take up!"</b></Default>

00:17:53.240 --> 00:17:54.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:17:55.740 --> 00:17:56.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mismis?</b></Default>

00:17:57.119 --> 00:17:58.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, Noro?</b></Default>

00:17:58.750 --> 00:18:00.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SHANOROTTE] Strange.
Why would a captain</b></Default>

00:18:00.410 --> 00:18:03.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the Imperial Army
be in the Central Province?</b></Default>

00:18:03.130 --> 00:18:05.089 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]
You're coming with me</b></Default>

00:18:05.170 --> 00:18:06.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
Hey, boss. This way!</b></Default>

00:18:09.380 --> 00:18:10.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[panting]
-[SHANOROTTE] Get back here!</b></Default>

00:18:11.470 --> 00:18:12.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That woman's Imperial!</b></Default>

00:18:13.339 --> 00:18:14.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Arrest her right away!</b></Default>

00:18:16.470 --> 00:18:18.099 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
I updated Lady Alice.</b></Default>

00:18:18.349 --> 00:18:20.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I reported that</b></Default>

00:18:20.269 --> 00:18:21.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was still missing</b></Default>

00:18:21.480 --> 00:18:23.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you found Schwartz
captured in the basement.</b></Default>

00:18:24.400 --> 00:18:26.569 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Right.
We took photos as proof.</b></Default>

00:18:27.190 --> 00:18:28.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

00:18:28.529 --> 00:18:30.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Proving that Lou's servant
is being held captive</b></Default>

00:18:30.819 --> 00:18:32.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by the Hydra family is huge.</b></Default>

00:18:32.990 --> 00:18:35.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It will be enough to make
Talisman back off.</b></Default>

00:18:36.529 --> 00:18:38.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, where is Salinger?</b></Default>

00:18:39.369 --> 00:18:40.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Salinger?</b></Default>

00:18:41.079 --> 00:18:43.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You didn't run into him
at Snow the Sun?</b></Default>

00:18:43.500 --> 00:18:46.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm. I haven't seen
any signs of him.</b></Default>

00:18:47.210 --> 00:18:48.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Interesting.</b></Default>

00:18:48.839 --> 00:18:50.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can use Snow the Sun's
surveillance footage</b></Default>

00:18:51.049 --> 00:18:52.299 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to try and find him.</b></Default>

00:18:52.930 --> 00:18:54.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
Okay, it opened.</b></Default>

00:18:55.220 --> 00:18:56.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here it is.</b></Default>

00:18:56.720 --> 00:18:57.599 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clicks]</b></Default>

00:18:58.140 --> 00:18:59.059 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NENE]
Hmm.</b></Default>

00:18:59.309 --> 00:19:02.099 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are two encrypted files
that look like bad news.</b></Default>

00:19:02.309 --> 00:19:04.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But there does appear
to be one that we can open.</b></Default>

00:19:05.599 --> 00:19:07.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN] What are these numbers
with symbols?</b></Default>

00:19:07.980 --> 00:19:09.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NENE]
Maybe the date and time?</b></Default>

00:19:09.819 --> 00:19:12.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it is, they left
the top place last night</b></Default>

00:19:12.779 --> 00:19:14.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then entered the Empire
territory this morning.</b></Default>

00:19:15.069 --> 00:19:17.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From the travel speed</b></Default>

00:19:17.950 --> 00:19:20.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder what sort of
payload they flew out?</b></Default>

00:19:20.329 --> 00:19:21.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Can't be.</b></Default>

00:19:21.500 --> 00:19:23.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are no airfields
in the direction</b></Default>

00:19:23.210 --> 00:19:24.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the plane's going.</b></Default>

00:19:24.410 --> 00:19:25.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, then what?</b></Default>

00:19:26.170 --> 00:19:28.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The symbols start
at Hydra's private property.</b></Default>

00:19:29.420 --> 00:19:31.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If a private plane
is leaving at this time</b></Default>

00:19:32.509 --> 00:19:33.839 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we may have a lead.</b></Default>

00:19:34.420 --> 00:19:35.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think it's her?</b></Default>

00:19:35.799 --> 00:19:36.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's Sisbell?</b></Default>

00:19:38.509 --> 00:19:39.599 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it is Sisbell</b></Default>

00:19:39.720 --> 00:19:41.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and we rescue her
from Empire territory</b></Default>

00:19:42.309 --> 00:19:44.309 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we could jeopardize
our status, too.</b></Default>

00:19:44.730 --> 00:19:46.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You pledged to rescue
Lady Sisbell.</b></Default>

00:19:47.269 --> 00:19:48.609 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's non-negotiable.</b></Default>

00:19:49.309 --> 00:19:50.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
We understand our mission.</b></Default>

00:19:51.150 --> 00:19:52.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But from our team's position</b></Default>

00:19:52.819 --> 00:19:55.859 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we can't infiltrate Imperial
territory like we did here.</b></Default>

00:19:56.319 --> 00:19:57.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Back me up, boss.</b></Default>

00:19:57.609 --> 00:19:58.779 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, he's right.</b></Default>

00:19:58.869 --> 00:20:00.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I also think helping you
directly puts us</b></Default>

00:20:00.990 --> 00:20:02.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in a compromised position.</b></Default>

00:20:02.829 --> 00:20:05.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a proposal
that may help us both.</b></Default>

00:20:05.750 --> 00:20:06.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're willing.</b></Default>

00:20:06.869 --> 00:20:08.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MISMIS]
Of course!</b></Default>

00:20:08.420 --> 00:20:11.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You may not have rescued
Lady Sisbell as promised</b></Default>

00:20:11.299 --> 00:20:13.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but we will still allow you
to leave, unharmed.</b></Default>

00:20:14.339 --> 00:20:15.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In exchange</b></Default>

00:20:15.339 --> 00:20:17.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you must agree
to one condition.</b></Default>

00:20:17.720 --> 00:20:19.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what condition is that?</b></Default>

00:20:19.599 --> 00:20:21.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To bring a Sovereign spy.</b></Default>

00:20:21.849 --> 00:20:23.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll return
to the Empire like normal</b></Default>

00:20:23.970 --> 00:20:25.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but with them in tow.</b></Default>

00:20:25.849 --> 00:20:28.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Sorry?
-That's not a bad idea.</b></Default>

00:20:28.480 --> 00:20:30.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly, it's the best
we can do</b></Default>

00:20:30.650 --> 00:20:32.319 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>given our current situation.</b></Default>

00:20:32.819 --> 00:20:33.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Exactly.</b></Default>

00:20:34.279 --> 00:20:36.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Basically, we'll leave
the Sovereignty</b></Default>

00:20:36.569 --> 00:20:38.069 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a spy following us.</b></Default>

00:20:38.450 --> 00:20:40.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once we cross
into Imperial territory</b></Default>

00:20:41.160 --> 00:20:42.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we wait.</b></Default>

00:20:42.279 --> 00:20:44.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take a long pause
outside the facility</b></Default>

00:20:44.200 --> 00:20:45.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where they're holding Sisbell.</b></Default>

00:20:45.829 --> 00:20:48.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then your spy will infiltrate
and do what they must, right?</b></Default>

00:20:48.750 --> 00:20:49.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

00:20:50.039 --> 00:20:51.339 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Boss, what do you think?</b></Default>

00:20:51.420 --> 00:20:53.339 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Considering we can't leave
the Sovereignty</b></Default>

00:20:53.420 --> 00:20:55.509 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>unless we agree
to this new proposal</b></Default>

00:20:55.589 --> 00:20:58.589 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's the only option we have</b></Default>

00:20:59.089 --> 00:21:00.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you understand...</b></Default>

00:21:00.549 --> 00:21:01.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>once we're inside</b></Default>

00:21:01.799 --> 00:21:03.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if your spy fails
to rescue Sisbell</b></Default>

00:21:04.009 --> 00:21:05.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's the end of the road.</b></Default>

00:21:05.349 --> 00:21:06.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We won't be able to help.</b></Default>

00:21:06.730 --> 00:21:09.059 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can't betray
the Empire any further.</b></Default>

00:21:09.440 --> 00:21:10.849 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I won't ask for more.</b></Default>

00:21:11.359 --> 00:21:12.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's on us at that point.</b></Default>

00:21:13.400 --> 00:21:14.819 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is all we can offer.</b></Default>

00:21:15.029 --> 00:21:16.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's our last negotiation.</b></Default>

00:21:19.569 --> 00:21:22.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If Lady Alice agrees
to the plan, we have a deal.</b></Default>

00:21:23.700 --> 00:21:25.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
I understand, Rin.</b></Default>

00:21:25.869 --> 00:21:29.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, let's move forward
with the plan you proposed.</b></Default>

00:21:29.579 --> 00:21:31.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be honest</b></Default>

00:21:31.579 --> 00:21:33.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I simply can't right now.</b></Default>

00:21:33.539 --> 00:21:35.089 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Under
the current circumstances</b></Default>

00:21:35.170 --> 00:21:37.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think it's best for you
to stay home.</b></Default>

00:21:37.670 --> 00:21:38.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know.</b></Default>

00:21:38.759 --> 00:21:40.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My mother needs me
by her side.</b></Default>

00:21:41.180 --> 00:21:42.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It must be a surrogate.</b></Default>

00:21:43.549 --> 00:21:45.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Right.
One that's qualified.</b></Default>

00:21:46.180 --> 00:21:48.599 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This spy will have
an immense responsibility.</b></Default>

00:21:49.019 --> 00:21:51.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They must understand
the current situation</b></Default>

00:21:51.440 --> 00:21:53.609 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and have the ability
to rescue Lady Sisbell</b></Default>

00:21:53.690 --> 00:21:55.109 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when the time comes.</b></Default>

00:21:55.190 --> 00:21:56.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, Rin!</b></Default>

00:21:56.609 --> 00:21:57.569 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For what?</b></Default>

00:21:57.650 --> 00:21:58.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
She's my sister.</b></Default>

00:21:59.319 --> 00:22:01.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can only assign
this mission to someone</b></Default>

00:22:01.359 --> 00:22:02.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I trust whole-heartedly.</b></Default>

00:22:03.200 --> 00:22:05.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, it has to be
someone you trust.</b></Default>

00:22:05.490 --> 00:22:07.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a sensitive matter.</b></Default>

00:22:07.200 --> 00:22:09.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which is why I was going
to suggest Kisasage--</b></Default>

00:22:09.500 --> 00:22:10.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
They won't do.</b></Default>

00:22:10.960 --> 00:22:12.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have strict criteria.</b></Default>

00:22:12.750 --> 00:22:14.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sobbing]</b></Default>

00:22:14.670 --> 00:22:16.799 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They must know Iska
and his team.</b></Default>

00:22:17.170 --> 00:22:18.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Officially</b></Default>

00:22:19.009 --> 00:22:21.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but in reality</b></Default>

00:22:21.839 --> 00:22:24.009 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen.
Lady Alice, please.</b></Default>

00:22:24.299 --> 00:22:25.349 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
What is it?</b></Default>

00:22:25.599 --> 00:22:27.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know this better
than anyone.</b></Default>

00:22:27.259 --> 00:22:29.809 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hate the Empire
to an astonishing degree.</b></Default>

00:22:30.269 --> 00:22:31.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just seeing their territory
on the map</b></Default>

00:22:32.019 --> 00:22:34.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>almost causes me
to convulse uncontrollably.</b></Default>

00:22:35.019 --> 00:22:37.069 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If someone like me
goes to the Empire</b></Default>

00:22:37.150 --> 00:22:38.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm afraid I'll...
[whimpering]</b></Default>

00:22:39.230 --> 00:22:42.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] I'm ordering you
to accompany Iska and his team</b></Default>

00:22:42.109 --> 00:22:44.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the Empire
and rescue Sisbell.</b></Default>

00:22:44.359 --> 00:22:45.819 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's an honorable mission.</b></Default>

00:22:45.910 --> 00:22:47.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're the only one
who can do it!</b></Default>

00:22:48.329 --> 00:22:50.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know
what you've gotta do, Rin!</b></Default>

00:22:50.369 --> 00:22:52.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] [crying]
But I don't wanna go!</b></Default>

00:22:53.869 --> 00:22:54.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:22:54.920 --> 00:22:57.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's gonna be okay</b></Default>

00:22:57.289 --> 00:23:03.799 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:23:08.559 --> 00:23:09.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Iska.
-Alice.</b></Default>

00:23:11.980 --> 00:23:13.059 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

00:23:14.269 --> 00:23:15.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE, ISKA]
Next stop.</b></Default>

00:23:15.769 --> 00:23:16.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE, ISKA]
The Empire.</b></Default>

00:23:18.859 --> 00:23:21.609 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>
